CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 9, 1967, pg.15 reads: "Home Again - Mrs. Alice Thompson and Mrs. Mayotis Johnson recently returned from attending the National Beauty Culturist League Convention is Atlanta, Ga. They motored down and stopped in Cincinnati, Ohio, and Asheville, N.C., to visit friends during the trip. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alice Thompson and Mayotis Johnson wearing name tags, standing beside car, another version
